    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个线性流程。我想确认一下：Docker镜像构建之后直接连到ServiceMesh，中间不需要经过镜像仓库或者CI/CD环节吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这里我们简化处理，聚焦在运行时架构。Docker镜像构建完成后直接进入ServiceMesh的服务发现层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Docker镜像和ServiceMesh连上了。接下来ServiceMesh到Serverless这一步，是表示流量接入无服务器函数吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_Serverless"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，ServiceMesh负责东西向流量治理，然后部分流量会路由到Serverless组件做弹性伸缩。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_Serverless"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "ServiceMesh到Serverless的连线已完成。现在Serverless到K8s集群，这里我有点疑问：Serverless通常是无服务器的，为什么还会落到K8s集群？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好问题。这里的Serverless是指Knative这类基于K8s的Serverless框架，底层还是需要K8s集群来承载Pod的，所以是Serverless控制平面落到K8s基础设施。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，Knative on K8s的模式。主线已经画好：Docker镜像→ServiceMesh→Serverless→K8s集群。接下来还有什么要补充的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
