    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个关键部分：每次代码提交后的持续部署循环。K8s集群部署完成后，会触发一个循环流程，包含多次Serverless和ServiceMesh的交互，最后再回到K8s。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个循环具体是什么含义？是蓝绿部署还是金丝雀发布？我需要理解清楚才能画准。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是金丝雀发布。每次提交后，K8s集群先触发Serverless的灰度版本，再验证，再切流量到另一个Serverless实例，然后经过ServiceMesh做流量权重调整，最后稳定后回归K8s集群状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个四步的循环子图：K8s→Serverless→Serverless→ServiceMesh。我用子图把循环部分框起来，标注为'LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "循环画好后，最后还需要一步：ServiceMesh把流量稳定后，重新调度回K8s集群做长期运行，然后再触发一次Serverless的清理或归档操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_Serverless"
