    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以循环结束后是：ServiceMesh→K8s集群→最后一个Serverless节点。这个Serverless是做什么的？",
      "elements_involved": [
